OL,3,CTwo charged with baby's 2023 murder
OL,5,FTwo people have been charged with
OL,6,Fmurdering an eight-week-old baby three
OL,7,Fyears after the infant's death.
OL,9,FThe baby died in hospital after police
OL,10,Fwere called to an address in Bourne,
OL,11,FLincolnshire, on 31 October2023.
OL,13,FLiam Neve, 26, of Spinney Close,
OL,14,FGrimoldby, Louth, and 26-year-old
OL,15,FLauren Murgatroyd, of Novak Place,
OL,16,FMorecambe, Lancashire, have both been
OL,17,Fcharged with murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
