OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1782481687
OL,3,CTwo charged with baby's 2023 murder
OL,5,FThey have also been charged with
OL,6,Fmaking a false statement concerning
OL,7,Fthe birth of a child, causing or
OL,8,Fallowing the death of a child, two
OL,9,Fcounts of causing grievous bodily
OL,10,Fharm, and two of causing or allowing a
OL,11,Fchild to suffer serious physical harm.
OL,13,FNeve has also been charged with two
OL,14,Fcounts of causing actual bodily harm.
OL,16,FThe pair are due to appear at Lincoln
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
