OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1782481687
OL,3,CTwo charged with baby's 2023 murder
OL,5,FDet Ch Insp Andy McWatt, of the
OL,6,FLincolnshire Police Major Crime Unit,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our thoughts are first and
OL,8,Fforemost with those impacted by this
OL,9,Fdeeply devastating case.
OL,11,F"This has been a complex and large-
OL,12,Fscale investigation, and we are now in
OL,13,Fa position to charge two individuals
OL,14,Fin connection with the incident.
OL,16,F"We recognise the deep distress this
OL,17,Fincident has caused and remain
OL,18,Fcommitted to seeking justice in memory
OL,19,Fof the baby who so tragically lost
OL,20,Ftheir life."
